{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a responsive Shopify section using **Liquid, HTML, CSS, and minimal JavaScript**.
    
    Section Name: **chat-with-astrologer-static**
    
    Goal:
    Design a **Chat With Astrologer listing page similar to the AstroTalk layout**, but all astrologer data should be **static inside the code** (not dynamic blocks, APIs, or Shopify data sources).
    
    Layout Requirements:
    
    1. Header Section
    
    * Title: **Chat With Astrologer**
    * Add a yellow underline below the title.
    * Add a search bar with placeholder **"Search name..."**.
    * Add a filter button icon.
    
    2. Category Filter Pills
       Create horizontal category buttons:
    
    All
    Love
    Education
    Career
    Marriage
    Health
    Finance
    
    Design:
    
    * Rounded pill buttons
    * Light grey background
    * Active pill should have **yellow background**
    
    3. Astrologer Card Grid
    
    Create a responsive grid layout:
    
    Desktop → 3 cards per row
    Tablet → 2 cards per row
    Mobile → 1 card per row
    
    4. Astrologer Card Design
    
    Each card should contain:
    
    Left Side
    
    * Circular astrologer image
    * Yellow border around image
    
    Right Side Content
    
    Name
    Example: Rudhran
    
    Specializations
    Example: Vedic, Lal Kitab, Face Reading
    
    Languages
    Example: English, Tamil
    
    Rating
    Show 5 star icons
    
    Experience
    Example: Exp: 5 Years
    
    Orders
    Example: 25914 orders
    
    Price per minute
    Example: ₹43/min
    
    Chat Button
    Green outline button with text **Chat**
    
    5. Badge Support
    
    Some cards should display badges on top:
    
    Rising Star
    Top Choice
    Verified (green tick icon)
    
    6. Static Data Requirement
    
    All astrologer cards must be **hardcoded inside the HTML** with example data like:
    
    Rudhran
    Arkes h
    Sanatan
    Devdat
    Shravika
    Neha09
    Kavishri
    Shivsagar
    Mohanm
    
    Do NOT use Shopify blocks, APIs, or dynamic loops.
    
    7. Card Style
    
    White background
    Rounded corners
    Soft shadow
    Padding
    Hover lift effect
    
    8. Responsive Behavior
    
    Cards must adjust correctly for desktop, tablet, and mobile screens.
    
    Output the complete **Liquid section code** ready to paste into:
    
    sections/chat-with-astrologer-static.liquid
    
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = 'chatastrologer' %}

{% style %}
  .ai-chat-astrologer-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: block;
    padding: 40px 20px;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ai-chat-astrologer-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }

  .ai-chat-astrologer-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 8px 0;
    color: #121212;
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .ai-chat-astrologer-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -8px;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 3px;
    background-color: #FFD700;
  }

  .ai-chat-astrologer-search-filter-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 24px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .ai-chat-astrologer-search-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex: 1;
    position: relative;
  }

  .ai-chat-astrologer-search-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .ai-chat-astrologer-filter-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: 12px 16px;
    background-color: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    border-radius: 8px;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .ai-chat-astrologer-filter-btn-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: #f9f9f9;
  }

  .ai-chat-astrologer-categories-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    margin: 24px 0;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .ai-chat-astrologer-category-pill-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: 8px 20px;
    background-color: #f3f3f3;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 14px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    color: #121212;
  }

  .ai-chat-astrologer-category-pill-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    background-color: #e8e8e8;
  }

  .ai-chat-astrologer-category-pill-{{ ai_gen_id }}.active {
    background-color: #FFD700;
    color: #121212;
  }

  .ai-chat-astrologer-grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
    margin-top: 30px;
  }

  .ai-chat-astrologer-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: #fff;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
  }

  .ai-chat-astrologer-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .ai-chat-astrologer-badge-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    top: 12px;
    right: 12px;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .ai-chat-astrologer-badge-{{ ai_gen_id }}.rising-star {
    background-color: #FFE5B4;
    color: #8B4513;
  }

  .ai-chat-astrologer-badge-{{ ai_gen_id }}.top-choice {
    background-color: #FFD700;
    color: #121212;
  }

  .ai-chat-astrologer-badge-{{ ai_gen_id }}.verified {
    background-color: #4CAF50;
    color: #fff;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .ai-chat-astrologer-card-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .ai-chat-astrologer-image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .ai-chat-astrologer-image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 3px solid #FFD700;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .ai-chat-astrologer-info-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .ai-chat-astrologer-name-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 6px 0;
    color: #121212;
  }

  .ai-chat-astrologer-specialization-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #666;
    margin: 0 0 4px 0;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .ai-chat-astrologer-languages-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #666;
    margin: 0 0 6px 0;
  }

  .ai-chat-astrologer-rating-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    gap: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .ai-chat-astrologer-star-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    color: #FFD700;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .ai-chat-astrologer-details-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #666;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

